'''Slicksuits''' were underwater survival suits made by the [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] and used for exploring [[Dac/Legends|Dac's]] [[Ocean/Legends|oceans]]. They were thin, skintight membranes made out of a glistening fabric. The suits provided temperature control, and a membrane at the back of the neck filtered oxygen molecules out of the ocean for breathing.

